snippet.title: Ni no Kuni: Wrath of the White Witch Remastered - E3 Announce Trailer | PS4, PC (Remastered); Switch
snippet.description:
Ni no Kuni: Wrath of the White Witch is coming to Nintendo Switch and remastered on PS4 & PC on 09.20.19. LEVEL-5’s classic tale is Remastered and also on-the-go! Follow Oliver’s journey as he embarks into a world inhabited by familiars and foes in the hopes of bringing back his mom.

Featuring music from Joe Hisaishi

#NiNoKuni #E32019 #BandaiNamco
